since when did I stop remembering,

277
00:19:19,062 --> 00:19:20,564
do you know?

278
00:19:21,732 --> 00:19:24,735
Umm, those things aren't important.

279
00:19:25,302 --> 00:19:27,738
Just being happy in each day,

280
00:19:28,272 --> 00:19:29,740
is enough.

281
00:19:32,643 --> 00:19:36,980
That's true, but I wanna get to know myself better.

282
00:19:41,551 --> 00:19:42,686
You still haven't went home?

283
00:19:50,827 --> 00:19:52,763
Hello, Talay.

284
00:19:53,830 --> 00:19:55,332
Talay?

285
00:19:56,300 --> 00:19:58,935
What were we like as kids?

286
00:20:03,373 --> 00:20:04,408
Just like this.

287
00:20:05,442 --> 00:20:06,442
And...

288
00:20:10,180 --> 00:20:11,848
did I dream to be a chef?

289
00:20:12,382 --> 00:20:13,382
Or..

290
00:20:14,017 --> 00:20:15,497
Do I have any other skills like this?

291
00:20:17,020 --> 00:20:18,889
Sometimes, when people ask..

292
00:20:19,323 --> 00:20:20,524
I also get curious.

293
00:20:25,329 --> 00:20:26,763
Hmm...

294
00:20:28,732 --> 00:20:30,772
You've dreamt of being a chef since you were young.

295
00:20:31,501 --> 00:20:33,303
Now you get to follow your dreams.

296
00:20:35,505 --> 00:20:36,540
And..

297
00:20:38,008 --> 00:20:39,810
Do I have a history with the ocean?

298
00:20:47,017 --> 00:20:50,354
Um, I think we should get going. Mom and Dad's waiting.

299
00:20:52,422 --> 00:20:53,690
Take care of the rest, Daiji.

300
00:20:56,093 --> 00:20:57,093
Goodnight.

301
00:21:19,483 --> 00:21:21,651
Tao Sor?

302
00:21:23,186 --> 00:21:24,186
Tao Sor!

303
00:21:25,255 --> 00:21:26,857
Yes?

304
00:21:27,891 --> 00:21:29,059
Umm...

305
00:21:29,526 --> 00:21:31,128
do we know each other?

306
00:21:31,828 --> 00:21:32,828
I'm Mor Kluen.

307
00:21:33,163 --> 00:21:34,331
I'm a friend of Talay's,

308
00:21:34,464 --> 00:21:36,099
as well as your regular doctor.

309
00:21:41,872 --> 00:21:42,873
And...

310
00:21:44,374 --> 00:21:45,742
are you studying for a test?

311
00:21:46,443 --> 00:21:47,443
Not at all...

312
00:21:47,544 --> 00:21:50,664
These days I've been looking through a lot of old research papers, that's all.

313
00:21:51,415 --> 00:21:55,619
Those Freud papers about the subconcious mind, those kind of things.

314
00:21:56,753 --> 00:21:57,788
Freud...

315
00:21:59,389 --> 00:22:00,389
Who's that?

316
00:22:00,724 --> 00:22:03,827
The person who said that our dreams are our true wishes confined,

317
00:22:04,161 --> 00:22:05,262
And to be honest,

318
00:22:05,896 --> 00:22:07,431
he seems pretty off in the head,

319
00:22:07,931 --> 00:22:09,531
but still a very interesting individual.

320
00:22:10,734 --> 00:22:12,202
Some times...

321
00:22:12,569 --> 00:22:14,704
dreams can tell us quite a lot.

322
00:22:15,305 --> 00:22:17,473
Especially the dreams that repeatedly come back,

323
00:22:17,474 --> 00:22:19,643
or ones that are unusually detailed.

324
00:22:21,545 --> 00:22:23,046
Repeated dreams...

325
00:22:24,648 --> 00:22:25,648
Then...

326
00:22:26,016 --> 00:22:28,351
if I dreamt that I fell into water..

327
00:22:29,386 --> 00:22:30,386
But...

328
00:22:30,854 --> 00:22:32,055
not in a painful way.

329
00:22:32,823 --> 00:22:33,823
Like...

330
00:22:34,991 --> 00:22:37,027
gradually sinking and...

331
00:22:37,627 --> 00:22:38,762
everything turned dark.

332
00:22:40,664 --> 00:22:42,365
Can that mean anything?

333
00:22:46,369 --> 00:22:47,537
Sometimes...

334
00:22:47,904 --> 00:22:49,506
it could be a sign of fear

335
00:22:50,407 --> 00:22:52,008
or things that have been unclear

336
00:22:52,576 --> 00:22:53,576
or unsual.

337
00:22:54,578 --> 00:22:56,313
Especially if the dream is cloudy.

338
00:22:58,448 --> 00:22:59,448
Or...

339
00:23:00,383 --> 00:23:03,386
Is me being afraid of the water and the ocean...

340
00:23:04,087 --> 00:23:05,388
because I've drowned before?

341
00:23:08,225 --> 00:23:09,225
When I was young,

342
00:23:10,393 --> 00:23:11,895
I couldn't remember anything.

343
00:23:12,562 --> 00:23:13,830
Umm.

344
00:23:15,532 --> 00:23:19,936
The memories will come back when we're ready.

345
00:23:20,904 --> 00:23:22,172
Then...

346
00:23:23,373 --> 00:23:26,376
that means, whenever we're ready...

347
00:23:28,345 --> 00:23:30,046
the dreams will get clearer, right?

348
00:23:31,982 --> 00:23:32,982
Mm!

349
00:23:34,584 --> 00:23:37,921
Then I won't bother you anymore.

350
00:23:39,456 --> 00:23:40,991
Till we meet again, Mor Kluen!

351
00:23:41,224 --> 00:23:42,224
Okay.

352
00:23:42,526 --> 00:23:44,227
If you dream of anything, you can tell me.

353
00:23:45,362 --> 00:23:46,530
Will do.

354
00:24:03,813 --> 00:24:04,813
Hello?

355
00:24:05,215 --> 00:24:08,285
Hey, we gotta talk. It's about Tao Sor.

356
00:24:13,490 --> 00:24:14,691
Snacks, Mr. Talay.

357
00:24:15,992 --> 00:24:16,992
Thanks alot.

358
00:24:24,668 --> 00:24:25,735
Mor,

359
00:24:26,369 --> 00:24:28,247
about what you said, about Tao Sor remembering things,

360
00:24:28,271 --> 00:24:31,374
about Tao Sor remembering things, just how much does he remember?

361
00:24:35,445 --> 00:24:37,347
It's not a continuous memory,

362
00:24:38,615 --> 00:24:39,816
it's kind of like...

363
00:24:41,384 --> 00:24:42,619
the suppressed memories...

364
00:24:43,353 --> 00:24:44,688
are so deep,

365
00:24:45,589 --> 00:24:48,429
that not even the owner of the memories knows what they're looking for.

366
00:24:51,027 --> 00:24:52,729
And if those memories come back,

367
00:24:53,463 --> 00:24:54,543
would that be a good thing?

368
00:25:01,538 --> 00:25:03,607
If it was a nice thing, then yes.

369
00:25:04,808 --> 00:25:06,528
But if it was something that caused pain...

370
00:25:07,410 --> 00:25:10,013
we'll have to accept that it's their right to remember

371
00:25:10,447 --> 00:25:11,514
according to human nature.

372
00:25:14,951 --> 00:25:16,831
But I don't want Tao Sor to be in pain anymore.

373
00:25:18,221 --> 00:25:19,221
That's up to you!

374
00:25:19,723 --> 00:25:20,723
But I suggest...

375
00:25:21,257 --> 00:25:25,629
sometimes not remembering at all is no different from running away?

376
00:25:25,829 --> 00:25:27,497
Right now, Tao Sor's having weird dreams.

377
00:25:27,664 --> 00:25:30,367
It's a sign that he's trying to communicate with his past self.

378
00:25:31,568 --> 00:25:33,336
If he sees the right thing,

379
00:25:34,270 --> 00:25:36,030
the thing he's been searching for all along,

380
00:25:36,373 --> 00:25:38,053
the memories will come back by themselves.

381
00:25:39,743 --> 00:25:42,779
And if that's the case, wouldn't that be even more dangerous?

382
00:25:48,184 --> 00:25:49,285
I'm just afraid.

383
00:25:50,453 --> 00:25:52,922
Afraid that if Tao Sor's memories do come back,

384
00:25:54,290 --> 00:25:55,659
nothing will be the same.

385
00:25:57,227 --> 00:25:59,629
Yeah, I understand.

386
00:26:00,530 --> 00:26:02,365
Although Tao Sor won't be the same,

387
00:26:02,932 --> 00:26:04,968
but he'll get to be his true self.

388
00:26:05,301 --> 00:26:07,337
Not the version we want him to be.

389
00:26:13,243 --> 00:26:15,912
And what if I don't want Tao Sor's memories to come back?

390
00:26:20,283 --> 00:26:24,320
You'd probably have to to be him a lot more.

391
00:26:24,788 --> 00:26:28,692
So he can focus on the present, and not the past.

392
00:26:44,541 --> 00:26:48,044
Chef Mochi, what are you doing? Not going home?

393
00:26:48,445 --> 00:26:49,579
Oh.

394
00:26:50,346 --> 00:26:52,191
I'm just preparing some Soy Sauce Pork Belly (Moo Hong)

395
00:26:52,215 --> 00:26:54,984
I saw that we'd be making Moo Hong tomorrow morning,

396
00:26:55,251 --> 00:26:56,853
so I wanted to start prepping today.

397
00:26:57,687 --> 00:26:59,823
But we don't have any classes tomorrow?

398
00:27:01,591 --> 00:27:04,160
What? There's no class?

399
00:27:07,297 --> 00:27:09,933
But I think I remember...

400
00:27:10,266 --> 00:27:12,869
a client saying that we'll be making Moo Hong tomorrow?

401
00:27:13,570 --> 00:27:14,704
You remember that?

402
00:27:17,340 --> 00:27:19,709
You must be confused, just wrap it up.

403
00:27:43,633 --> 00:27:45,168
Is something wrong, Mom?

404
00:27:45,268 --> 00:27:47,704
Your brother's looking strange these days, Talay...

405
00:27:48,171 --> 00:27:49,672
I couldn't stop worrying.

406
00:27:50,974 --> 00:27:54,544
Is there anything going on with your brother? Have you guys gone anywhere lately?

407
00:27:56,980 --> 00:27:57,980
No.

408
00:28:04,387 --> 00:28:07,991
He's drawing these strange pictures, I have a bad feeling about this.

409
00:28:11,327 --> 00:28:12,629
It's nothing, Mom.

410
00:28:13,863 --> 00:28:15,031
You don't have to be worried.

411
00:28:16,566 --> 00:28:18,067
I'll take care of everything.

412
00:28:19,068 --> 00:28:23,706
I think maybe we should take him out to do something new?

413
00:28:48,932 --> 00:28:51,901
Wait here for a minute, okay? We're gonna find something to eat.

414
00:28:53,603 --> 00:28:55,905
Wait here, we'll be back!

415
00:29:20,997 --> 00:29:24,601
Tao Sor!

416
00:29:29,772 --> 00:29:30,772
Sorry?

417
00:29:33,142 --> 00:29:34,210
Do we know each other?

418
00:29:35,578 --> 00:29:37,046
I missed you so much.

419
00:29:38,214 --> 00:29:39,214
Do you remember you?

420
00:29:40,817 --> 00:29:41,818
Who are you?

421
00:29:42,418 --> 00:29:43,418
I'm Kim!

422
00:29:50,493 --> 00:29:51,493
Get over here!

423
00:29:51,661 --> 00:29:53,496
Hey, what's this?
- Come!

424
00:29:55,098 --> 00:29:55,999
What's your deal?

425
00:29:56,000 --> 00:29:58,468
Didn't I tell you to stop messing with Tao Sor?

426
00:29:59,402 --> 00:30:00,403
I'm not threatening you..

427
00:30:01,004 --> 00:30:02,004
I'll do it for real.

428
00:30:02,105 --> 00:30:03,539
I really don't understand you.

429
00:30:04,173 --> 00:30:06,733
Just letting your brother remember what happened the day before,

430
00:30:06,910 --> 00:30:07,910
how's that a bad thing?

431
00:30:08,811 --> 00:30:10,371
That's because you don't know anything!

432
00:30:10,847 --> 00:30:12,382
What Tao Sor had to go through...

433
00:30:12,982 --> 00:30:14,050
cause you're simpleminded.

434
00:30:14,784 --> 00:30:15,784
But it's a good thing

435
00:30:16,286 --> 00:30:17,646
that he doesn't remember anything.

436
00:30:18,721 --> 00:30:20,056
Doesn't remember that he...

437
00:30:22,292 --> 00:30:24,227
got with a horrible person like you.

438
00:30:25,495 --> 00:30:26,696
Me and Tao Sor

439
00:30:27,030 --> 00:30:28,331
were consensual to each other.

440
00:30:29,198 --> 00:30:31,067
And I do feel like I love him.

441
00:30:31,467 --> 00:30:32,467
Love?

442
00:30:32,869 --> 00:30:34,570
How can you dare say that you love him?

443
00:30:35,538 --> 00:30:36,773
Look at what you did!

444
00:30:37,540 --> 00:30:39,342
You made him confused.

445
00:30:40,176 --> 00:30:41,611
If I wasn't there that day,

446
00:30:42,178 --> 00:30:44,213
who knows where he'd be by now.

447
00:30:46,182 --> 00:30:47,502
But did he choose to go with you?

448
00:30:48,217 --> 00:30:49,652
Or did you decide for him?

449
00:30:50,386 --> 00:30:51,688
- You little...
I love Tao Sor!

450
00:30:56,092 --> 00:30:57,860
He loves me?

451
00:31:04,167 --> 00:31:06,869
Let Tao Sor forget those feelings along with you!

452
00:31:09,605 --> 00:31:11,307
I've proven to Tao Sor,

453
00:31:11,774 --> 00:31:13,643
that I would be his memory for him!

454
00:31:30,593 --> 00:31:34,630
Whoa, I was gonna bring you some beer,
but you're already set.

455
00:31:36,099 --> 00:31:37,333
You're late!

456
00:31:37,667 --> 00:31:39,235
I was working, yes?

457
00:31:40,303 --> 00:31:41,303
I don't believe you.

458
00:31:45,475 --> 00:31:47,195
You were with your girlfriend, weren't you?

459
00:31:47,543 --> 00:31:48,845
What girlfriend?

460
00:31:49,946 --> 00:31:52,515
So what's with you? You look stressed out.

461
00:31:59,255 --> 00:32:01,257
I miss him, Siw!

462
00:32:02,825 --> 00:32:04,193
Miss who?

463
00:32:04,594 --> 00:32:06,062
Well, who else?

464
00:32:07,463 --> 00:32:08,664
It's Tao Sor!

465
00:32:09,065 --> 00:32:10,166
Ahh...

466
00:32:10,433 --> 00:32:14,103
You mean the chef at the resort?
- Yeah..

467
00:32:14,604 --> 00:32:16,806
Well, if you miss him then do something!

468
00:32:17,774 --> 00:32:19,342
You can't just be pouting like this.

469
00:32:19,842 --> 00:32:22,712
Go see him, or just call him if he's busy.

470
00:32:23,346 --> 00:32:24,747
You gotta do something, Kim!

471
00:32:24,914 --> 00:32:26,382
I'm hammered already, Siw!

472
00:32:26,616 --> 00:32:28,117
What do you want me to do?

473
00:32:28,418 --> 00:32:31,754
Every time I go to him, his brother just pushes me away!

474
00:32:32,455 --> 00:32:35,391
He said that I'm dangerous.

475
00:32:35,925 --> 00:32:40,029
So what're you gonna do? You can't just be drinking beer here like this!

476
00:32:46,235 --> 00:32:47,870
Do you have a better idea?

477
00:32:47,937 --> 00:32:50,339
Each day, he acts more like a stranger...

478
00:32:50,473 --> 00:32:51,993
This is a straight up One Night Stand!

479
00:32:52,308 --> 00:32:53,308
Huh?!

480
00:32:53,976 --> 00:32:55,445
What are you talking about?

481
00:32:55,745 --> 00:32:57,480
Kim, calm down.

482
00:32:58,548 --> 00:33:01,017
So what did he do to you?

483
00:33:04,954 --> 00:33:06,355
1 day.

484
00:33:07,557 --> 00:33:08,858
Tao Sor...

485
00:33:09,559 --> 00:33:11,661
can only remember things for 1 day.

486
00:33:12,795 --> 00:33:14,063
Once he wakes up,

487
00:33:14,764 --> 00:33:17,733
he forgets everything about the day before, Siw!

488
00:33:18,935 --> 00:33:21,537
People like this exist?

489
00:33:23,239 --> 00:33:26,542
Then that means, even if you go see him,

490
00:33:26,576 --> 00:33:29,412
there's no guarantee that he'll remember you?

491
00:33:29,779 --> 00:33:30,779
Yes.

492
00:33:34,684 --> 00:33:35,284
But...

493
00:33:35,485 --> 00:33:37,220
I've actually never tried.

494
00:33:38,721 --> 00:33:39,822
It might work?

495
00:33:45,094 --> 00:33:47,430
You luck in love looks really good!

496
00:33:47,597 --> 00:33:48,297
Really?

497
00:33:48,498 --> 00:33:51,666
It says they'll be a medium to help you achieve your goals.

498
00:33:51,667 --> 00:33:54,069
Medium... like...

499
00:33:54,070 --> 00:33:55,470
Cupid or something?

500
00:33:55,471 --> 00:33:56,471
Yes!

501
00:34:02,378 --> 00:34:03,513
Kim!

502
00:34:03,880 --> 00:34:06,883
I'll be your own Cupid.

503
00:34:12,655 --> 00:34:14,857
Alright, what you want me to do? I'm ready.

504
00:34:15,625 --> 00:34:18,461
Is everyone ready? Today we'll be making Moo Hong.

505
00:34:20,096 --> 00:34:21,464
It's pork belly.

506
00:34:24,100 --> 00:34:25,268
Wait for me!

507
00:34:34,443 --> 00:34:36,345
Umm...

508
00:34:36,779 --> 00:34:37,480
Your name...

509
00:34:37,481 --> 00:34:40,483
Oh, this is the new student that just booked.

510
00:34:40,750 --> 00:34:41,750
Ohh...

511
00:34:43,286 --> 00:34:44,587
Where did you come from?

512
00:34:47,790 --> 00:34:51,794
Umm, her name is Kimchi. She's from South Korea.

513
00:34:51,961 --> 00:34:55,798
And she loves Southern food, so she booked a course with us.

514
00:34:56,232 --> 00:34:57,633
Ohh...

515
00:34:58,034 --> 00:35:00,436
Okay, there's another set available,

516
00:35:00,636 --> 00:35:02,705
you can join the class.
- Thank you so much!

517
00:35:02,838 --> 00:35:04,774
Kimchi from South Korea?

518
00:35:06,442 --> 00:35:09,312
We're gonna be making Moo Hong, and these are our ingredients,

519
00:35:09,412 --> 00:35:12,415
pork belly, garlic, pepper and...

520
00:35:12,615 --> 00:35:14,483
over there are the different seasonings.

521
00:35:14,717 --> 00:35:17,820
You can now slice the pork belly.

522
00:35:52,855 --> 00:35:55,858
Thank you all for being so cooperative.

523
00:35:56,025 --> 00:35:58,194
Let's make another menu soon.

524
00:35:58,461 --> 00:36:00,162
Thank you, Chef!
- Thank you, Chef!

525
00:36:02,431 --> 00:36:04,267
Umm, just a moment.

526
00:36:04,533 --> 00:36:05,533
Why...

527
00:36:06,435 --> 00:36:08,104
do you seem so familiar?

528
00:36:11,507 --> 00:36:12,642
We might have...

529
00:36:13,042 --> 00:36:14,310
Crossed paths before?

530
00:36:14,977 --> 00:36:16,245
R.really?

531
00:36:18,281 --> 00:36:19,882
Would you recall..

532
00:36:20,349 --> 00:36:22,218
The person who acted as your rmemories?

533
00:36:25,588 --> 00:36:27,657
I used to be your memory.

534
00:36:32,795 --> 00:36:33,795
But...

535
00:36:33,963 --> 00:36:35,283
Doesn't seem to be like that now.

536
00:36:36,532 --> 00:36:37,633
W..wait a minute.

537
00:36:38,534 --> 00:36:41,237
Can you tell me about the day we met?

538
00:36:41,537 --> 00:36:42,705
Tao Sor!

539
00:36:43,572 --> 00:36:44,573
Chef Tao Sor,

540
00:36:44,840 --> 00:36:48,344
If you're free tonight, come to Siam Sea's port. You'll know everything.

541
00:36:49,478 --> 00:36:50,478
Let's go!

542
00:36:59,121 --> 00:37:00,423
You good? How was it today?

543
00:37:00,556 --> 00:37:02,191
It was.. okay.

544
00:37:03,492 --> 00:37:04,493
Umm...

545
00:37:05,795 --> 00:37:06,795
Talay?

546
00:37:08,464 --> 00:37:09,465
Tonight...

547
00:37:10,099 --> 00:37:11,500
can I go out?

548
00:37:12,301 --> 00:37:12,835
Of course!

549
00:37:13,302 --> 00:37:15,022
Where do you wanna go? I'll take you there.

550
00:37:15,271 --> 00:37:16,472
Umm...

551
00:37:18,374 --> 00:37:22,511
I'm sorry, the time for Siam Sea's trip is over now.

552
00:37:22,712 --> 00:37:25,514
But the clients in Rooms 504 and 508,

553
00:37:25,781 --> 00:37:28,551
