554
00:37:28,984 --> 00:37:31,187
Of course, I'll have the driver send them.

555
00:37:31,554 --> 00:37:31,921
Umm..

556
00:37:32,421 --> 00:37:34,590
It seems like the driver isn't here.

557
00:37:35,524 --> 00:37:36,524
Really?

558
00:37:38,027 --> 00:37:39,662
Y..yes.

559
00:37:42,398 --> 00:37:44,300
Okay, then I'll take them myself.

560
00:37:45,534 --> 00:37:47,536
Tao Sor, If there's anything, call me, okay?

561
00:37:48,037 --> 00:37:49,238
S..sure!

562
00:37:50,706 --> 00:37:51,706
Let's go.

563
00:38:32,381 --> 00:38:35,718
Even though you can't remember me, that's fine.

564
00:38:48,030 --> 00:38:49,198
But...

565
00:38:49,732 --> 00:38:51,734
can we just stay like this for a while?

566
00:38:54,470 --> 00:38:55,905
I don't know what...

567
00:38:57,873 --> 00:38:59,308
happend to me.

568
00:38:59,909 --> 00:39:00,909
But...

569
00:39:01,343 --> 00:39:04,346
why do I recognize the...

570
00:39:04,547 --> 00:39:06,015
scent...

571
00:39:07,416 --> 00:39:08,818
the feeling on my skin...

572
00:39:10,786 --> 00:39:12,221
Who...

573
00:39:12,855 --> 00:39:14,190
exactly are you?

574
00:39:20,262 --> 00:39:21,664
Why don't you...

575
00:39:22,198 --> 00:39:25,201
use your feelings to answer that question?

576
00:39:34,477 --> 00:39:35,478
Tao Sor!

577
00:39:36,779 --> 00:39:37,779
Do...

578
00:39:38,414 --> 00:39:39,748
you remember me?

579
00:39:44,954 --> 00:39:46,522
No, I don't. Just...

580
00:39:47,623 --> 00:39:48,623
I just felt it.

581
00:39:50,559 --> 00:39:51,560
It's okay.

582
00:39:52,361 --> 00:39:53,361
Because I...

583
00:39:54,296 --> 00:39:56,365
will be your memories for you.

584
00:39:57,299 --> 00:39:58,834
How can I remember you...

585
00:39:59,902 --> 00:40:01,537
I don't even remember who I am.

586
00:40:03,672 --> 00:40:05,140
In that case...

587
00:40:05,474 --> 00:40:07,076
do you trust me?

588
00:40:10,579 --> 00:40:11,947
Trust me, okay?

589
00:40:13,015 --> 00:40:16,318
I'm gonna take you on a trip through our memories together.

590
00:40:31,834 --> 00:40:34,703
In the end, your readings were accurate.

591
00:40:34,870 --> 00:40:36,138
Siwy the Cupid.

592
00:40:45,915 --> 00:40:48,884
For sure, the other thing was also accurate.

593
00:40:49,752 --> 00:40:51,120
Which thing?

594
00:40:53,455 --> 00:40:57,359
The one that says that your love is right in front of you.

595
00:42:01,056 --> 00:42:03,592
When 2 blue whales meet,

596
00:42:03,926 --> 00:42:06,095
it's like meeting a certain person,

597
00:42:07,062 --> 00:42:08,564
in our wide and large world,

598
00:42:08,998 --> 00:42:10,633
that truly understands us.

599
00:42:12,468 --> 00:42:13,636
Have we ever made love?

600
00:42:13,802 --> 00:42:14,803
Do...

601
00:42:15,738 --> 00:42:16,739
you trust me?

602
00:42:17,139 --> 00:42:18,216
Where'd did you find this out?

603
00:42:18,240 --> 00:42:19,240
Oh..

604
00:42:19,441 --> 00:42:20,275
Me and...

605
00:42:20,276 --> 00:42:21,844
Don't tell me...

606
00:42:22,344 --> 00:42:23,078
Kim...

607
00:42:23,312 --> 00:42:24,947
Getting to meet Kim,

608
00:42:25,581 --> 00:42:27,516
is the best thing that's ever happened to me.

609
00:42:33,656 --> 00:42:34,823
And...

610
00:42:35,124 --> 00:42:37,693
how do you know if you've ever had any better experiences?

611
00:42:39,561 --> 00:42:41,063
I love you, Kim!

